room_title: Escape room "Zodiac Serial Killer" by Fox in a Box Seattle in Seattle
room_description: You are captured by a serial killer. Tied up and left in his apartment , escape is your only chance. His method of operation is much like one Infamous Zodiac killer had. Has the real Zodiac returned or is this his copycat? You have only 60 minutes to escape, or the next body in a morgue will be yours.
